	   <tr><td colspan=2>If you still find yourself using Supperior Healing a lot still (and not just CH) you may want to do the Fine Antique Veil quest in the PoK Museum.&nbsp;&nbsp;It's has Improved Healing II on it and since your obtain all your standard healing spells before Lvl 40 it's a fine focus item until you cease using SH.<br>&nbsp;<br>Heelem, Froglok Cleric<br>Squwaker, Vah Shir Beastmaster<br>Gilwedar, Woodelf Ranger<br><br>-- The Nameless --</td></tr>
